result.title: Codeforces Round #287: Division 2
result.content:
Hi all,

Just a friendly reminder that there is CF Round #287 today for Division 2 folks. Take it, dominate it, and come back here discuss it :)

HidenoriS will lead the discussion today, as I have a schedule conflict for the contest unfortunately. I promise that I would come back and do the problems and join the discussion afterwards.

Remember: you will be promoted to Division 1 if you solve ABC fast enough and perhaps D!

Best of luck folks!

yongwhan
